<item>
            <title>[LU-7052] iovec created with iov_iter_get_pages_alloc must be freed with kvfree</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7052</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Commit 98883bd3e2cc48a3a5674ce140ad74bece37df05 added support for iov_iter_get_pages_alloc for newer kernels, instead of ll_get_user_pages. However the iovec was still freed within ll_free_user_pages, using OBD_FREE_LARGE. Use kvfree instead (like in the linux kernel).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="31753">LU-7052</key>
            <summary>iovec created with iov_iter_get_pages_alloc must be freed with kvfree</summary>
